WHAT?!!! pic.twit

description:
It’s unclear how any serious person can vote for someone like Rep. Jasmine Crockett, given her objective naivety, but she does not have a shortage of foolish things to say.

During her swearing-in ceremony, she appeared to be somewhere between the first and second stages of grief regarding the presidential election. At first, she tried to rationalize Kamala’s loss, claiming that people should have voted for her because no one is perfect. However, several minutes into her unhinged rant, she turned this into a racial issue and made up some statistic that claims “80 percent of extreme crimes are committed by white supremacists.”

Rep Jasmine Crockett says Trump brought evil to the White House, suggests his voters are all white supremacists, and so are all J6ers.
title: Democrat congresswoman gets sworn in, immediately suggests Trump voters are all white supremacists
